      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented test suite covering hemolysis scalar transport; independent review of build and release procedures required at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver is version-controlled and unit tests exist, but no independent audit of the build pipeline has been performed and the hemolysis scalar transport module lacks a dedicated regression suite. Achieved level 2 falls short of required level 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Method of manufactured solutions (MMS) applied to all governing equations including the hemolysis damage accumulation transport equation; order-of-accuracy confirmed.",
      "rationale": "MMS verification was applied to the Navier-Stokes solver but not extended to the hemolysis power-law transport equation. Spatial order of accuracy is unconfirmed for the damage model. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
