      "rationale": "A three-level grid convergence study was completed and GCI computed for pressure rise and flow uniformity, but GCI for the hemolysis index QoI specifically reaches 11% on the medium mesh and 7% on the fine mesh, exceeding the 5% threshold. Achieved level 3 against required level 4."
    },
    {
