      "rationale": "Iterative residual targets were set to 1e-4 for momentum equations but no analysis of round-off or iterative error contributions to the hemolysis scalar was performed. This factor was not assessed; flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5. Achieved level 1 against required level 4."
