      "acceptanceCriteria": "Formal justification of turbulence model selection (SST k-ω vs. LES) and hemolysis power-law exponent choice for blood in high-shear rotating machinery; sensitivity analysis across plausible model forms required.",
      "rationale": "SST k-ω turbulence model was used without formal comparison to higher-fidelity alternatives. The hemolysis power-law exponents were taken from a single literature source without sensitivity analysis. Model form uncertainty is the dominant unknown at MRL 5 and was not formally assessed. Achieved level 1 against required level 5."
    },
